# sessions/ — BRD §4.5 tree-structured session storage
#
# Sessions auto-save per turn. Each session: sessions/<project>/<session_id>.json
# containing the full tree (turns + branches + labels).
#
# Archived transcripts (for the Compactor subagent, BRD §4.3):
#   sessions/archive/<session_id>/transcript.json
#
# /tree, /fork, /branch, /export commands operate on these files.
